KubeEdge提供了一个容器化的边缘计算平台，该平台具有内在的可伸缩性。由于模块化和优化的设计，它是轻量级的(较小的占用空间和运行内存)，可以部署在低资源的设备上。同样，边缘节点可以具有不同的硬件结构和不同的硬件配置。对于设备连接，它可以支持多个协议，并使用标准的基于MQTT的通信.这有助于有效地扩展具有新节点和设备的边缘集群。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>K8S中的CRD开发</title><link>http://bingerambo.com/posts/2021/05/k8s%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84crd%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/</link><pubDate>Tue, 04 May 2021 08:43:17 +0800</pubDate><author>作者</author><guid>http://bingerambo.com/posts/2021/05/k8s%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84crd%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/</guid><description>&lt;p>介绍K8S使用CRD进行开发的操作步骤。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>编译kube-batch和density</title><link>http://bingerambo.com/posts/2021/03/%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91kube-batch%E5%92%8Cdensity/</link><pubDate>Wed, 31 Mar 2021 08:43:17 +0800</pubDate><author>作者</author><guid>http://bingerambo.com/posts/2021/03/%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91kube-batch%E5%92%8Cdensity/</guid><description>&lt;p>编译kube-batch项目和自己开发的压测工具density。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>业务压力测试tsung-in-k8s</title><link>http://bingerambo.com/posts/2021/03/%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E5%8E%8B%E5%8A%9B%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95tsung-in-k8s/</link><pubDate>Mon, 08 Mar 2021 08:43:17 +0800</pubDate><author>作者</author><guid>http://bingerambo.com/posts/2021/03/%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E5%8E%8B%E5%8A%9B%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95tsung-in-k8s/</guid><description>&lt;p>在K8S中部署业务压力测试工具tsung，修改并进行了自测验证&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>K8S常用操作命令集合</title><link>http://bingerambo.com/posts/2021/02/k8s%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Feb 2021 08:43:17 +0800</pubDate><author>作者</author><guid>http://bingerambo.com/posts/2021/02/k8s%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88/</guid><description>&lt;p>K8S常用操作命令集合，持续更新~~~&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>kubelet volume manager源码分析</title><link>http://bingerambo.com/posts/2021/02/kubelet-volume-manager%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90/</link><pubDate>Thu, 25 Feb 2021 08:43:17 +0800</pubDate><author>作者</author><guid>http://binger